    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:0",
      "text": "Common Tab 提供 Maya 中所有 renderer 共享的设置。请注意，此配置会在将 RenderMan 设为 renderer 后，或从 RenderMan menu 打开设置后显示。",
      "ascii_letters": 51,
      "cjk_chars": 31
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:2",
      "text": "Workspace Tab",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:6",
      "text": "File Name",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:8",
      "text": "Workspace Tab",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:10",
      "text": "Image Size",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:11",
      "text": "显示 resolution（通常以 pixels 和 inches 表示）。",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:12",
      "text": "Color Management",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:13",
      "text": "RenderMan 不支持 Output Transform 设置。不过，\"it\" 中提供了 view",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:14",
      "text": "remapping",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:16",
      "text": "File Output",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:17",
      "text": "渲染图像文件名最多可由三个元素组成：file name、frame number 和 file format。",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:18",
      "text": "File Name Prefix",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:20",
      "text": "Image Format",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:23",
      "text": "会设置显示用的 display driver。",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:24",
      "text": "Compression",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:25",
      "text": "不适用；AOVs tab 会在 Display Driver 中设置 compression。",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:26",
      "text": "Frame/Animation Ext",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:27",
      "text": "用于命名 output images 的格式。",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:28",
      "text": "Frame Padding",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:30",
      "text": "Framebuffer/Naming Scheme",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:32",
      "text": "Use Custom Extension",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:34",
      "text": "Frame Range",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:35",
      "text": "Start Frame, End Frame",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:38",
      "text": "rendered frames 的 output names 之间的增量。只有当 Frame/Animation Ext 设为包含 # 的选项时，By Frame 才可用。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:39",
      "text": "Renderable Cameras",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:40",
      "text": "Renderable Camera",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:42",
      "text": "如果场景只有一个 renderable camera（例如 perspective camera），无论在这个 drop-down list 中选择哪个 camera，它都会成为 renderable camera。换句话说，新选择的 camera 会成为场景中的 renderable camera（默认 perspective camera 会变为不可渲染）。",
      "ascii_letters": 106,
      "cjk_chars": 49
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:43",
      "text": "Alpha Channel (Mask)",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:44",
      "text": "确定 rendered images 是否包含 mask channel。",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:45",
      "text": "Depth Channel (Z Depth)",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:46",
      "text": "确定 rendered images 是否包含 depth channel。建议使用 AOVs tab 指定 __depth 或 Z。",
      "ascii_letters": 39,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:47",
      "text": "Image Size",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:49",
      "text": "根据行业标准预设选择 output images 的 resolution。",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:50",
      "text": "Maintain Width/Height Ratio",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:51",
      "text": "如果勾选此框，custom resolutions 会保持锁定的 height/width ratio。禁用此参数后，可以为 image resolution 输入任意数值。",
      "ascii_letters": 48,
      "cjk_chars": 27
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:52",
      "text": "Width/Height",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:53",
      "text": "对于 custom resolutions，请在此处输入所需的 resolutions。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:54",
      "text": "Size Units",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:55",
      "text": "选择合适的 measurement unit。",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:56",
      "text": "Resolution",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:57",
      "text": "设置图像的 rendered resolution。",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:58",
      "text": "Resolution Units",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:59",
      "text": "选择 resolution 的定义单位，可以是 pixels per inch 或 pixels per centimeter。",
      "ascii_letters": 42,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:60",
      "text": "Device Aspect Ratio",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:61",
      "text": "target display（例如 \"it\" 或 Maya's Render View）的 aspect ratio。",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:62",
      "text": "Pixel Aspect Ratio",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:63",
      "text": "显示 device 上单个 pixels 的 aspect ratio，也就是你查看 rendered image 时所用设备的像素纵横比。",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:64",
      "text": "Render Options",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:65",
      "text": "Enable Default Light",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:66",
      "text": "在 rendering 期间开启或关闭 default lighting。请注意，如果场景中有 RenderMan lights，我们不会 render default light。",
      "ascii_letters": 57,
      "cjk_chars": 21
    },
    {
      "item_id": "0d8282ff1f:67",
      "text": "Pre/Post MEL scripts",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    }
  ],
